{"tid":279391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚悚！學生飆車撞貨車　眼球爆出懸掛臉頰 圖","createTime":"2017-06-11T08:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T15:00:37.000Z","uid":72009,"like":8,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9829746beffcb5bb5d63108d7d98777446a15880","tid":279391,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"《鳳凰網》報導，這起車禍都被路上監視器給拍下，當時這名男學生騎著機車在路上極速狂飆，在撞上貨車的前一刻也未緊急煞車，就這樣撞上載滿鐵條的貨車，導致鐵條直接插入他的眼部，且整個人坐在機車上靠著鐵條無法動彈。靠近一看，一顆眼球更遭到擠壓而爆出來掛在臉頰，滿臉鮮血直流，事後當地警方獲報，立刻前往事發現場並將男學生送醫治療。據了解，警方初步研判，貨車因為載貨超出車體所限，恐會承擔事故的部分責任，詳細事故情形仍有待進一步調查釐清。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170611/640_2b9b896f24d77c568faa59086ca26b7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170611%2F640_2b9b896f24d77c568faa59086ca26b7f.jpg&h=fdf42ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243eb3e7aba8d2e3bf651f47862593125ecf37ab","tid":279391,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"二世祖？"},{"pid":"59781fd7636d5703cf5ae27e686e234d48e3c8de","tid":279391,"uid":61882,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>父精母血，不可棄也！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c2de7d11062fcea99b90c380ca8daf350f0a5b60","tid":279391,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"冇格呢"},{"pid":"9f40c9f3e6fc6e5bc92ea10ee511ff269e169acf","tid":279391,"uid":441,"like":4,"dislike":39,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"小心 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e61a7e3724181f9e1e3983580d9e8c6589c3919","tid":279391,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets